## Architecture

Clean Architecture with strict layering. The **Dependency Rule** is non-negotiable:
source-code dependencies always point **inward**.

```text
presentation/infrastructure -> application -> core
```

| Layer | Directory | May Import From |
| --- | --- | --- |
| Core | `backend/src/{{ project_slug }}/core/` | stdlib, utils/ only |
| Application | `backend/src/{{ project_slug }}/application/` | core/, utils/ |
| Infrastructure | `backend/src/{{ project_slug }}/infrastructure/` | core/, application/ |
| Presentation | `backend/src/{{ project_slug }}/presentation/` | application/, core/ (exceptions, enums) |
| Config | `backend/src/{{ project_slug }}/config/` | core/enums/, utils/ |
{%- if use_ai %}
| AI | `backend/src/{{ project_slug }}/ai/` | core/, application/, utils/ |
{%- endif %}
| Utils | `backend/src/{{ project_slug }}/utils/` | stdlib ONLY |

