## Task Runner

All commands use [Task](https://taskfile.dev/):

```bash
task dev              # Start full development stack
task test             # Run all tests (backend + frontend)
task lint             # Lint all code
task format           # Format all code
task typecheck        # Type-check all code
task build            # Production build
task registry:generate  # Regenerate constants from naming_registry.json
```

## Conventions Summary

- **Python**: snake_case, type hints everywhere, structured logging (structlog),
  keyword-only args, `raise ... from e`, no `Final[]`, no `Any`
- **TypeScript**: PascalCase components, camelCase functions, strict mode
- **Shell**: zsh only (`.zsh` extension), `emulate -L zsh`, `setopt PIPE_FAIL ERR_EXIT`
- **Commits**: Conventional Commits (`type(scope): description`)
- **Constants**: Never hardcode; use `registry/naming_registry.json`
- **Docs**: Google-style docstrings, module-level docstrings mandatory

